==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: wŏ bú rù dìyù, shéi rù dìyù
===Idiom===
'''[[我]][[不]][[入]][[地獄]]，[[誰]][[入]][[地獄]]'''
# If I don't do it, who will?; If I don't help, who will?; Sacrifice oneself in order to save others
===Alternative forms===
[[我不入地狱，谁入地狱]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
